Quote:Is this one of the 4-pack sealed, 30 card minimum decks?That would make a little more sense given he has exactly four flip cards. Though he's still short a rare unless I keep missing one.That said, as much as I dislike the combination I'd go WR. You are going to run something like 12 or 13 lands, so you need to come up with about 17 playables. I'd try something along the lines of:Thraben HereticSilverchase FoxUnruly MobLoyal CatharMidnight GuardChapel GeistThrabel PurebloodsKessig WolfPyreheart WolfRusset WolvesTormented PariahNearheath StalkerBurden of GuiltGeistflameRolling TemblorFaithless LootingRolling Temblor is super sketch since it basically kills all your dudes, but sometimes you just need a reset button. The other option would be Mask, but it's so slow that I don't know that it's going to help you. Otherwise you can maindeck Urgent Exorcism. There are enough spirits and enchantments that it's honestly not terrible in the main.
